WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:13.116
<b>To begin installation, open a terminal and navigate or create an installation directory</b>

2
00:00:13.116 --> 00:00:17.849
<b>Type "python" in the terminal to verify its installation</b>

3
00:00:17.849 --> 00:00:22.699
<b>Type "exit()" to exit</b>

4
00:00:22.699 --> 00:00:28.883
<b>Type "git" in the terminal to verify its installation</b>

5
00:00:28.883 --> 00:00:33.349
<b>Type "git init" to create an empty repository</b>

6
00:00:33.349 --> 00:00:41.516
<b>Type "git clone https://github.com/C2311231/SkySpindle.git" to download files</b>

7
00:00:46.650 --> 00:00:53.266
<b>Change to the downloaded directory ("cd ./SkySpindle")</b>

8
00:00:55.783 --> 00:01:11.949
<b>Create a virtual environment "python -m venv ./SkySpindleEnv"</b>

9
00:01:13.349 --> 00:01:24.766
<b>Activate the virtual environment "./SkySpindleEnv\Scripts\activate.bat"</b>

10
00:01:25.150 --> 00:01:26.699
<b>Install the dependencies "pip install -r requirements.txt"</b>

11
00:01:26.699 --> 00:01:40.266
<b>Run SkySpindle "python main.py"</b>

12
00:02:11.283 --> 00:02:16.883
<b>You may have to allow access to the network</b>

13
00:02:26.016 --> 00:02:35.250
<b>Connect to your CNC machine, and the installation is complete</b>
